A simple simulation of planets, in our solar system, orbiting around the Sun using
basic physics, Newton's law of gravitation and Velocity Verlet.

Rendered using Bevy game engine.

Skybox from: https://tools.wwwtyro.net/space-3d/index.html
Textures from: https://www.solarsystemscope.com/textures/

